.TH budgie-screensaver 1 "2021\-04\-21" "Solus"
.SH NAME
budgie-screensaver \- screen saver and locker
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B budgie-screensaver
.RI [ OPTIONS... ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Budgie Screensaver is the default screen saver and locker in a Budgie
desktop. It is designed with simplicity and security in mind.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-no\-daemon
Don't become a daemon
.TP
.B \-\-debug
Enable debugging code
.P
This program also accepts the standard GTK options.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR "gtk-options" (7)

